Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\N this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly \Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:26.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:30.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:30.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:34.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:34.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:39.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:39.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:45.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:45.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:50.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:50.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:55.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:55.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:59.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:00:59.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:02.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:02.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner (･∀･)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:05.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner :D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:05.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:11.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:11.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:16.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:19.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:23.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:23.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:27.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:27.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
